Name.en: Is Dog Weight Loss & Diabetes W1 safe for dogs with allergies or intolerances?

FAQ reference - Answer.en: Dog Weight Loss & Diabetes W1 is free from the following common allergens: dairy, lamb, fish, egg, wheat, maize, soya and gluten. If in doubt, ask your vet if this food is suitable for your dog.
